N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1085.9 - Presentation of tickets

State Regulations

No person shall refuse or fail to present a valid

Metro-North ticket, employee pass or dependent pass, or tender the applicable
fare, as required. Notes
